      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound E46 M3 powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L straight-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. This example utilizes the sought-after 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and factory M-Variable differential. The VANOS system has been serviced, and the rear subframe\u2014a known weak point\u2014has been inspected and reinforced. Suspension components feature upgraded polyurethane bushings for sharpened turn-in. While showing minor cosmetic wear consistent with an enthusiast-driven life, the drivetrain is dialed in for peak performance. A true driver\u2019s car with a transparent maintenance history.",
